description: Trading and algorithmic trading platform (stock markets, forex, bitcoins and options). .NET wrapper for InteractiveBrokers, GainCapital, IQFeed, Oanda, FIX/FAST, QUIK etc. More info on web site https://stocksharp.com/products/api/
releaseNotes:
Alerts. Message made optional for sound based events.
ISecurityAssociationStorage added.
Bithumb. Prime service supported.
OKEX. Support turn on/off sections.
IQFeed. Candles request fixes.
FIX connector. IFixDialect tick as level1 option.
Process non persistable basket securities.
Storage adapter. Fix boards lookup and update.
IPositionStorage added.
Reduced IEntityRegistry usage.
Diagram. Multiple sockets for logical condition added.
TraderHelper. Filter positions by PortfolioLookupMessage.
ServicesRegistry added.
ExpressionIndexSecurityProcessor fix.
FixServer. FixSecurityLegsRequestMessage, FixSecurityLegsResultMessage messages added.
Reconnection fix.
IMessageAdapter.IsSupportSecuritiesLookupAll overriding fix.
Digifinex, Idax, TradeOgre connectors.
ITakeProfitOrderCondition, IStopLossOrderCondition, IWithdrawOrderCondition.
CsvEntityRegistry. Currency and ExpirationDate added.
SubscriptionMessageAdapter. IsRestoreOnNormalReconnect added.
News. Priority property added.
CoinCap connector.
Coinigy connector.
FIX connector. IBKR dialect supported algo orders.
FixServer. Support SecurityStatusRequest.
OKEx. Web sockets v3 supported.
Plaza CGate. Spectra 6.2 supported.
TWIME. Spectra 6.2 supported.
Micex TEAP. Interface 31 supported.
Storage lists. WaitFlush added. Removed ReadLasts.
Statistics parameters. Fix reset state.
MarketDepthControl. Fix processing quote msgs with empty instrument info.
RSS fixes.
MarketDepthControl. Dynamic change price/volume text formats.
UnitEditor refactoring.
OpenECry. More order types supported.
OKEX. Position and account swap and margin supported.
Candles compression. Fix for non TF candles compression.
Basket adapter. Fix processing pending connect subscriptions.
Connector. Fix subscribers counter for error responses.
IConnector. MarketDataUnexpectedCancelled event added.
Basket adapter. Support offline mode for dedicated adapters.
SampleBitfinex. Candles added.
ActionMessage. Message for iterate actions.
BoardEditor redesign.
MessageAdapter. Fix ReConnectionSettings save/load.
PropertyGridEx. WorkingTime supported.
OpenECryException removed.
Connector. Clear portfolio lookup criteria fix.
Simulator. Turn off heartbeat tracking for non owned adapters https://stocksharp.ru/posts/m/46473/
Order. IsManual property added.
LBank, BitMax, BW, Bibox, CoinBene, BitZ, ZB connectors.
Heartbeat. Restore after reconnect.
Deribit. Extended orders.
Diagram. More options for order registration.
CurrencyTypes. MXP added.
IConnector. LookupXXXResult2 overloads.
AlphaVantage. Lookup instruments supported.
Quik. Fix hands while instruments lookup https://stocksharp.ru/forum/9238/zavisaet-quik-pri-podklyuchenii/
Fix security lookup.
Basket adapter. Fix lookup processing.
MessageAdapter. Time out fixes.
